t:
I've a power,I can see the future.

Panicking, I tried to warn the other passengers that this plane will crash, but no one understood.




They're just annoyed; no one likes a crying baby on a plane.
c:
Somewhere, in an underground office, some people will be celebrating the death of the baby; they've just stopped a superhero from growing up.
